{"tid":2324073,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔夠兩個星期就到聖誕","createTime":"2020-12-13T16:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T02:15:42.000Z","uid":370062,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"547a819f0bf999c9b8f261a2d067cd6806c58b25","tid":2324073,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"希望各位連登巴絲可以開開心心過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論親情友情定愛情都可以一直保持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕當日約咗屋企人朋友另一半嘅玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未約嘅希望你哋快啲約到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溝緊仔或女嘅希望你哋快啲溝到然後甜甜蜜蜜過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之希望大家今年過個開心愉快幸福嘅聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好好似本行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077c30fcdea52d4ecf1de03c495f3eca7debbe16","tid":2324073,"uid":383593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"日日倒數日日見<br />\n係咪完左聖誕你就唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e168fb24bb600b72d94cc4784d697be0f37981af","tid":2324073,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"077c30fcdea52d4ecf1de03c495f3eca7debbe16","tid":2324073,"uid":383593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"日日倒數日日見<br />\n係咪完左聖誕你就唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"完咗聖誕我就繼續開假膠po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78272fe0db207e407355aca0e466b48439a24a4","tid":2324073,"uid":376618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eaa68a9a5008ee0ed4